      'Bug fix: print view abilities panel shows only abilities the player has purchased — optional psyker upgrades and choice-gated abilities hidden until bought.',
      'Bug fix (CSM): Malicious Volley trait now correctly applies Deflagrate(5+) to Heavy Bolters and all Bolt weapons.',
